Helen Gilmore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Gilmore 0 Helen Gilmore (1900 – October 8, 1947) was an American actress of the stage and silent motion pictures from Chicago, Illinois. She left acting to become a magazine editor. Helen_Gilmore ( 1900 – October_8_,_1947 ) was an_American_actress of the_stage and silent_motion_pictures from Chicago , Illinois .
